quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  40,8,"Joomi amen, naaduɓe ka Aljannaaji ñiiɓal, ɗin ɗi foduɗaa ɓe, e kala moƴƴuɗo e baabiraaɓe maɓɓe, e genndiraaɓe maɓɓe, e geyngol maɓɓe. Pellet, ko An woni Fooluɗo, Ñeeñuɗo On"
  40,9,"Daɗndaaɓe [kuuɗe] e bonɗe ɗen. Kala mo daɗnduɗaa [kuuɗe] mun bonɗe ɗen nden Ñalnde, haray pellet, A yurmiii mo\". Ko ɗum woni maloore mawnunde nden"
  40,10,"Yedduɓe ɓen noddiroyte: \"Ko tikkere Allah nden ɓuri mawnude, e dii ko tikkanɗon ko'e mon kon, tuma noddetenoɗon e gomɗinal, yeddon"
  40,11,"Ɓe wi'a: \"Joomi amen, A warii men laawi ɗiɗi, wuurnituɗaa men laawi ɗiɗi: men qirrike junuubi amen ɗin. Taw si laawol yaltirngol hino woodi"
  40,12,"Ɗum mooɗon, ko tawde si Allah tun noddanooma, on yeddon; si O kafidaama, gomɗinon. Ñaawoore nden ko Allah heeranii, Toowuɗo, Mawɗo On"
  40,13,"Ko Kanko woni holloowo on maandeeji Makko ɗin, O jippinirana on toɓo ka kammu. Kono taskotaako, si wanaa ruttotooɗo [e Allah]"
  40,14,"Rewiree Allah, laɓɓinirangol Mo diina kan, hay si heeferɓe ɓen yiɗaa"
  40,15,"Ko o toowuɗo darjaaji, Jeyɗo Arsi kin. Himo jippiniria wahayu on, yamiroore Makko, e on mo O muuyani e jeyaaɓe Makko ɓen, no o jertinira ñalnde Kawral ngal, @Corrected"
  40,16,"ñalnde ɓe feeñoyta. Huunde suuɗotaako Allah, e fee maɓɓe. Ko hommbo laamu woodani hannde? Ko Allah Bajjo, Fooluɗo On"